What you need to know:  From the rally modified cars to the normal road cars, KICC played host to quite a number of petrol heads who were in for treat of both man and machineThe highlight of the day was 12-year-old, future formula 1 champion, Zahran Mogul, who blessed the crowd all day with his quite special skills in go-kartingFIA Rally Star, Hamza Anwar thanked organisers of the WRC Motor Expo saying it is the best way to easily expose their sponsors to the limelight